beer.beer_description: Paradise Pils! Inspired by Nat’s trip to the Pilsner cellars of Bohemia. A self-confessed IPA-fiend, everything that Nat believed to be true was challenged the fateful day he drank unfiltered Pilsner in the cellars of Urquell. Since then he has been working towards putting a unique KAIJU! spin on this classic lager style. Paradise Pils brings crisp palate perfection layered with fruity new world, German and US hops
